# Cloudflare Pages — HTTP response headers applied to every route.
# This is the STRICT production CSP: script-src and style-src are hash-locked
# ('sha256-...') instead of 'unsafe-inline', so injected inline scripts/styles are
# blocked. The hashes cover the exact MINIFIED bytes of the inline blocks Hugo
# emits (theme toggle, menu/top-link/reading-progress scripts, code-copy, and the
# two <style> blocks). application/ld+json data blocks aren't script-src-governed,
# so they need no hash.
#
# MAINTENANCE: if you edit the inline reading-progress script/style in
# layouts/_partials/extend_head.html, OR bump HUGO_VERSION / the PaperMod submodule
# (either can change the minified bytes), these hashes go stale and the affected
# inline block gets blocked (theme toggle / reading bar / code-copy silently break).
# Regenerate with:  ~/Desktop/my_scripts/csp-hashes.sh  and paste the tokens below.
# The <meta> CSP in layouts/_partials/extend_head.html is deliberately kept LOOSE
# ('unsafe-inline') as the local `hugo server` preview fallback (preview isn't
# minified, so these production hashes wouldn't match it); in production both
# policies are enforced, so this stricter header still does the blocking.
# NOTE: if you enable GoatCounter analytics later, also add
#   https://gc.zgo.at  to script-src   and   https://*.goatcounter.com  to img-src + connect-src.
/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' https://giscus.app 'sha256-bOIlT+8wbFz3AQtUEup46zzMyMh8mHc3lD1pmMtpJD8=' 'sha256-UBD9lfFHKxagKGHh9S8B2hytN1cmDsFK1Tl1uedsZ0Q=' 'sha256-5ilQRTfItUB+Etsk1onTDCqBA1OpUBIKfJhdMlZ61Co=' 'sha256-/cFFbEHjTjpj7DLefsC+h1yhrxRRebLCB86XtBuCtvw=' 'sha256-KHyHOOpYOFHylRCfkAjr3t7Ej1N6ByeUULOPShxcySo=' 'sha256-eyUVosQAviXm2qeOTG819D1n0kSst2gY8VmfgVsZlag='; style-src 'self' https://giscus.app 'sha256-TzlBu+Yp5QndAbgUwjajid8QyFloMLEZVV3SLr0syao=' 'sha256-YXSIknXFQPLWhafTW99LWkZVzoCwLoQZz7UboAWhuDg='; font-src 'self'; img-src 'self' data: https://avatars.githubusercontent.com; connect-src 'self' https://giscus.app; frame-src https://giscus.app; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'
